However, he tried to lead the
situation to his advantage

260
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:54,380
and tried to use that
recording as his evidence.

261
00:20:54,380 --> 00:20:56,480
That's why I requested a
disciplinary committee hearing.

262
00:20:56,480 --> 00:21:00,640
You mean only the part that made
you culpable was recorded?

263
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:02,810
You're a repeat offender.

264
00:21:02,810 --> 00:21:04,550
This is already your second time.

265
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:08,740
Without any proof nor any witnesses,
why do you keep bothering Prosecutor Hong?

266
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:11,180
That's what I want to ask him.

267
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:13,270
Why is he continuing to do that to me?

268
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:16,460
Now that we're talking about the past,
I think it's becoming clear to me.

269
00:21:17,650 --> 00:21:20,330
When she was a trainee,
her performance was subpar,

270
00:21:20,330 --> 00:21:21,620
so she only did grunt work.

271
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:24,970
She also received the
lowest scores possible.

272
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:29,260
