00:28:16,430 --> 00:28:17,900
♫ It may hurt ♫

375
00:28:33,410 --> 00:28:35,720
How are you doing in here?

376
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:40,450
How is the firm?

377
00:28:40,450 --> 00:28:42,650
There is some movement
among the shareholders.

378
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:47,810
They'll want my shares turned
over to the company

379
00:28:47,810 --> 00:28:50,530
and for me to step aside.

380
00:28:50,530 --> 00:28:52,960
I don't think the movement will last long.

381
00:28:54,590 --> 00:28:56,860
Why aren't you asking me for it?

382
00:28:58,040 --> 00:29:00,640
- What are you...
- The shares.

383
00:29:03,020 --> 00:29:05,220
You are at the center of this right now,

384
00:29:05,220 --> 00:29:07,570
so you should be asking me
to hand them over.

385
00:29:07,570 --> 00:29:10,450
If I asked, would you give them to me?

386
00:29:10,450 --> 00:29:11,880
If I gave them to you,

387
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,480
do you have confidence?

388
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:16,230
If I'm confident, will you give them to me?

389
00:29:20,390 --> 00:29:22,110
Was it you

390
00:29:22,110 --> 00:29:24,320
who made your father like this?

391
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:27,310
Besides you,

392
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:30,860
I don't know anyone else who would
have had tax evasion records.

393
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:33,040
If I say no,

394
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:34,780
would you believe me?

395
00:29:36,100 --> 00:29:38,440
You would not believe me.

396
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:40,870
Father, you have never

397
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:44,520
trusted me, not once.

398
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:46,210
Is that why you did this?

399
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:50,060
If you pushed me out,

400
00:29:50,060 --> 00:29:52,700
did you think the firm would be yours?

401
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:54,500
Yes.

402
00:29:54,500 --> 00:29:56,670
Really...

403
00:29:57,810 --> 00:29:59,550
you did this.

404
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:02,740
Yes.

405
00:30:09,690 --> 00:30:11,910
I raised you as a son.

406
00:30:13,810 --> 00:30:15,740
But you are just garbage.

407
00:30:19,820 --> 00:30:21,980
Have you ever told me

408
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:26,430
that I did a good job?

409
00:30:27,740 --> 00:30:30,460
Ever given me praise?

410
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:33,240
Have you ever patted your son's head?

411
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:38,530
Never, not even once.

412
00:30:40,250 --> 00:30:43,540
What more do I need to do?

413
00:30:43,540 --> 00:30:45,120
That's why...

414
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:48,350
you should have done well!

415
00:30:54,830 --> 00:30:56,040
Yes.

416
00:30:57,020 --> 00:30:58,550
Yes.

417
00:31:03,220 --> 00:31:06,400
I'm sorry that I was not
good enough for you.

418
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:08,190
Father.

419
00:31:08,190 --> 00:31:10,690
When will you grow up?
